540вҶ’// Regression: StatsNotInflatedByMultipleSessions
541вҶ’//
542вҶ’// The old code counted stats inside the per-client send loop:
543вҶ’//   for (client : clients_in_group) {
544вҶ’//     if (send_binary(client, data)) {
